{"type": "article", "id": 8977, "title": "Google 为了打败专利流氓，开了一个在线专利市场", "description": "“专利流氓”让不少大公司都吃尽苦头，Google 能解决这个顽疾吗？", "date": "2015-04-28T14:18:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 9458, "name": "专利流氓"}, {"id": 199, "name": "Google"}, {"id": 68, "name": "苹果"}, {"id": 536, "name": "三星"}, {"id": 9459, "name": "RPX"}], "category": 4, "author": 43366, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604223105CQ1pbsRr2LHw74VZ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t没有任何产品、却搜罗各种专利用于起诉别人的公司，一般被称为“专利流氓”（<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Patent Troll</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）。苹果、</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Google </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">等巨头都吃过他们的苦头：苹果去年 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">2 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月输给 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Smartflash LLC </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">公司<a href=\"http://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/2015/02/25/company-without-a-product-wins-533m-verdict-vs-apple-says-its-no-patent-troll/\" target=\"_blank\">一场 </a></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><a href=\"http://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/2015/02/25/company-without-a-product-wins-533m-verdict-vs-apple-says-its-no-patent-troll/\" target=\"_blank\">5.33 </a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><a href=\"http://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/2015/02/25/company-without-a-product-wins-533m-verdict-vs-apple-says-its-no-patent-troll/\" target=\"_blank\">亿美元的专利官司</a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">；</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Google </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在卖掉摩托罗拉之前，也不停面临起诉，从 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">2011 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">到 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">2014 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年，</span><a href=\"http://www.theverge.com/2014/2/4/5375304/intellectual-ventures-goes-to-trial-against-google-and-motorola\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Intellectual Ventures </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">公司告了 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Google </span></a><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><a href=\"http://www.theverge.com/2014/2/4/5375304/intellectual-ventures-goes-to-trial-against-google-and-motorola\" target=\"_blank\">和摩托罗拉三次</a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.rpxcorp.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">根据反“专利流氓”公司 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">RPX </span></a><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><a href=\"http://www.rpxcorp.com/\" target=\"_blank\">的说法</a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，单是 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">2014 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年全球因这类专利诉讼损失的诉讼费就高达 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">122 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">亿美元。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t一般来说，大公司之间的“专利战”往往能取得一定平衡，比如当年苹果起诉三星侵犯专利时，三星也能以类似的诉讼加以还击。相当一部分大公司之间的专利纠纷都会以相互授权专利的形式解决。可面对那种没有任何实体产品、没法告的公司，巨头们的“诉讼反击”就无能为力了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t为了从源头上扼杀“专利流氓”，<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Google 宣布</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">推出试验性的专利交易平台“</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><a href=\"http://www.google.com/patents/licensing/\" target=\"_blank\">Patent Purchase Promotion</a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，让持有美国专利的个人直接向 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Google </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">兜售自己的专利。</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Google </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">专利问题法律顾问  </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Allen Lo 在</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><a href=\"http://googlepublicpolicy.blogspot.com/2015/04/announcing-patent-purchase-promotion.html\" target=\"_blank\">昨天发表的博客中</a>认为</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">：“这有望为专利持有人创造更好的体验，并消除‘专利流氓’引起的混乱局面。”</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t新<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Patent Purchase Promotion </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">平台将在 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">5 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">8 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">日到 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">22 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">日之间开放，专利持有人可以在网上向 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Google </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">提交申请，并为自己的专利定个价，目前范围还仅限于在美国注册的专利。</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Google </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">称他们将在平台关闭之后查看每一份申请，遇到感兴趣的，会在 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">6 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">26 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">日前通知申请人。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><a href=\"http://static.googleusercontent.com/media/www.google.com/zh-CN/us/patents/licensing/doc/patent-palooza-more-information.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Google </a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><a href=\"http://static.googleusercontent.com/media/www.google.com/zh-CN/us/patents/licensing/doc/patent-palooza-more-information.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">发布的具体日程安排</a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">显示，随后 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Google </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">会要求这些被选中的申请人在 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">7 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">8 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">日前提交有关专利的更多详细信息。如果一切顺利，</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Google </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">预计会在 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">7 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">22 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">日前掏钱买下中意的专利。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\tGoogle <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">认为专利市场长期混乱的一个原因在于不少专利持有人将专利卖给“专利流氓”，因此他们希望用 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Patent Purchase Promotion </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">平台将专利交易的过程公开，直接和专利持有人建立联系。不过这个项目现在还只是试验性的，结果如何尚难以定论。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<a href=\"%EF%BC%88http://www.wired.com/2015/04/google-wants-buy-patent-keep-away-trolls/\" target=\"_blank\">《连线》杂志在报道中认为</a><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，这个专利交易平台还能为 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Google </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">提供更多有价值的信息，比如当前市面上还有哪些专利、它们价值几何等等。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t同时，<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Patent Purchase Promotion </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">平台还可能成为 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Google </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的专利防御系统。所谓专利防御系统，就是通过收购专利授权给客户，以免其陷入专利诉讼的泥淖中，类似的公司有 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><a href=\"http://www.rpxcorp.com/\" target=\"_blank\">RPX</a> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">等等。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t不过说起来，<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Intellectual Ventures </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">最早也是一个专利防御系统，甚至 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Google </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">还给它投过最初的启动资金，而今却成了<a href=\"http://www.theverge.com/2014/2/4/5375304/intellectual-ventures-goes-to-trial-against-google-and-motorola\" target=\"_blank\">全球最大、最著名的“专利流氓”</a>。如果 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Patent Purchase Promotion </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">平台试验成功并逐渐成型，也可能成为 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Google </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">对付其它科技巨头的“弹药库”。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">此前 Google 在专利战方面一直扮演防御角色，没有主动攻击竞争对手的习惯，但未来如果形势发生变化，不知道还会不会保持“不作恶”？</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t图片来源：<span style=\"color:#3D3C40;font-family:Lato, appleLogo, sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;\"><a href=\"http://www.hellorf.com/\" target=\"_blank\">站酷海洛创意</a></span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}